Class CloudListFragment

    public class CloudListFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements BackButtonListener
    Mostly configures a contained {RecyclerView}. {CloudListFragment}, {CloudListAdapter}, and {CloudListViewHolder} work together to create the cloud sources list.
    See Also:
    https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/layout/recyclerview
